quest.name: Good Hunting
journal: The Allagan tracking node is awaiting user interaction.
The Allagan tracking node appears to be conducting some sort of training program and has challenged you to hunt down four empuses.
You hunt down the empuses as instructed. Return to the tracking node for your performance evaluation.
It seems the tracking node is unable to complete its training program. Given next week's hunting target, that may very well be for the best...
